{"tid":2096285,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國椰奶製品悲慘真相！ PETA踢爆：猴兒充當摘椰工","createTime":"2020-07-06T04:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T04:59:36.000Z","uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0406d17cc5d708b13ab59a955941ca30e08d5a60","tid":2096285,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cache.hkgolden.media/compress/http://www.grandprix.co.th/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/chaokoh_liverpool_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcache.hkgolden.media%2Fcompress%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.grandprix.co.th%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fchaokoh_liverpool_2.jpg&h=d67df530&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://the18.com/sites/default/files/feature-images/Liverpool-Coconut-Water.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthe18.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Ffeature-images%2FLiverpool-Coconut-Water.jpg&h=b32134ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你在超市買過從泰國進口的椰奶等椰子製品嗎？國際動保組織成員臥底踢爆負責採摘椰子的「猴子工人」，竟有非法盜捕而來的嬰猴，這些猴工不僅總是被鎖鏈拴住，生活環境也相當髒亂，農場主人甚至坦承，這些猴工往往都是摘椰子摘到生命結束，永遠沒有退休的一天。<br />\n<br />\n國際動保組織「PETA亞洲 」7月3日發布新聞稿指出，臥底成員在泰國椰奶品牌「Chaokoh」的椰子供應地造訪了4間猴子學校、8座椰子農場及一場摘椰子比賽，貼身挖掘猴工的生活狀況。<br />\n<br />\n從PETA拍攝的影片可看到，猴工總是被鎖鏈牢牢拴住，沒有自由活動的時間。此外，牠們經常只能待在狹小的籠子裡，生活環境也十分髒亂。一名農場主人甚至直言這些猴子往往都是一直工作到死亡為止。顯見牠們永遠沒退休的一天。<br />\n<br />\nPETA指出，成員訪查的猴工當中甚至還有遭非法盜捕而來的嬰猴，牠們被迫爬上棕櫚樹採摘椰子，然後出口到世界各地。PETA主席紐柯爾克（Ingrid Newkirk）表示，他們認為幾乎所有來自泰國的椰子都是受虐猴子所採摘，呼籲人們購買其他產地的椰子製品。<br />\n<br />\n由於報導內容令人震撼且痛心，總部在美國加州的進口連鎖零售商「Cost Plus World Market」率先表態其國內276間實體店鋪和網路商店將停售泰國「Chaokoh」的產品，歐美等地也有多家大型超市和商店響應，連泰國品牌「Aroy-D」的產品也遭停售。<br />\n<br />\n針對歐美等品牌及商場抵制泰國椰奶產品一事，泰國商務部常任秘書本亞里對泰國媒體表示，目前已展開多部門協調溝通。泰國猴工是因應當地農民生活方式所衍生出來的特有產業，將會邀請各國大使實地參觀椰子農場的採摘狀況，力圖消弭雙方誤會。<br />\n<br />\n部分台灣網友認為這種景象在泰國其實很常見，沒什麼大不了；但大部分網友仍覺得猴子的生活素質太差勁，人類不應該這樣對待幫助他們生計的動物。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4BZOnTMrRms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4BZOnTMrRms&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FqHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=f58a3075\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4BZOnTMrRms</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/member/twdaily/article/1_1764232__1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fmember%2Ftwdaily%2Farticle%2F1_1764232__1&d=HclisOHeH6vmzOJk9j96FqHX%2F1llhPerIglyOgZNoj0%3D&h=27786c9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fmember%2Ftwdaily%2Farticle%2F1_1764232__1&h=61d091b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/member/twdaily/article/1_1764232__1</a>"},{"pid":"1e1d32608867ad8022e3624849a90cf1af26d276","tid":2096285,"uid":100069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:43:33.000Z","msg":"Karl pilkington: monkey news"},{"pid":"457409ecd71b336dce2d4116288a303bfa9796cd","tid":2096285,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:44:23.000Z","msg":"屌 利狗又迫害"},{"pid":"0922a2455e7d5cda59770a5fea4d87629fec156f","tid":2096285,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"457409ecd71b336dce2d4116288a303bfa9796cd","tid":2096285,"uid":38189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:44:23.000Z","msg":"屌 利狗又迫害"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:46:32.000Z","msg":"利狗打壓完人權依家連猴權都打壓埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705bf6cb9a08d04d3039be03ef96b369c0d9dc84","tid":2096285,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:47:01.000Z","msg":"岩岩買咗兩盒"},{"pid":"5b5a4b1e186623c085fe3df5506b6625b32d8d5f","tid":2096285,"uid":86199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"中國大米製品悲慘真相！LIHKG踢爆：牛兒充當耕田工"},{"pid":"4c8f5c3413f5a2f366a744141547ae94e7adfde7","tid":2096285,"uid":99700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T04:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c5hrdct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-sr